<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''红霉素'''（{{lang-la|'''Erythromycin'''}}）是一种[[大环内酯|大环内酯]]类的[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]<ref name=AHFS2015/>，可用於治療[[呼吸道感染|呼吸道感染]]、{{tsl|en|skin infections|皮膚感染}}、衣原體菌感染（{{lang-la|chlamydia infections}}），以及[[梅毒|梅毒]]<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。本品也可用於預防新生兒的{{tsl|en|Group B streptococcal infection|B群鏈球菌感染}}<ref name=AHFS2015/>。紅黴素可以用於改善胃輕癱（{{lang-la|gastroparesis}}）的症狀<ref>{{cite journal | authors = Camilleri M, Parkman HP, Shafi MA, Abell TL, Gerson L | title = Clinical guideline: management of gastroparesis | journal = The American Journal of Gastroenterology | volume = 108 | issue = 1 | pages = 18–37; quiz 38 | date = Jan 2013 | pmid = 23147521 | doi = 10.1038/ajg.2012.373 }}</ref>。本品可透過靜脈注射或口服給藥<ref name=AHFS2015/> 。新生兒有時會給予含有紅黴素的眼藥水，以避免新生兒結膜炎（{{lang-la|neonatal conjunctivitis}}）<ref>{{cite journal | authors = Matejcek A, Goldman RD | title = Treatment and prevention of ophthalmia neonatorum | journal = Canadian Family Physician | volume = 59 | issue = 11 | pages = 1187–90 | date = 2013-11 | pmid = 24235191 }}</ref>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
常見副作用包含腹絞痛、嘔吐，以及腹瀉等<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。更嚴重者可能引發[[偽膜性結腸炎|偽膜性結腸炎]]、肝臟疾病、[[長QT症|長QT症]]，以及[[過敏|過敏反應]]<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。[[青黴素|青黴素]]過敏者通常可安全服用本品<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Erythromycin|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/erythromycin.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=2015-08-01|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091751/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/Erythromycin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[妊娠|妊娠]]期間用藥目前顯示安全<ref name=AG2015>{{cite web|title=Prescribing medicines in pregnancy database|url=http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm#.U1Yw8Bc3tqw|work=Australian Government|date=August 23, 2015|access-date=2016-08-24|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408040902/http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm#.U1Yw8Bc3tqw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般認為[[母乳餵養|哺乳]]期間用藥為安全，但有研究顯示，未滿兩周的新生兒若服用本品，或母體於哺乳期間用藥，可能會增加罹患[[幽門狹窄|幽門狹窄]]的風險<ref name=Ric2013/><ref name="Kong2013">{{cite journal|vauthors=Kong YL, Tey HL |title=Treatment of acne vulgaris during pregnancy and lactation|journal=Drugs |volume=73 |issue=8 |pages=779–87|date=June 2013|pmid=23657872|doi=10.1007/s40265-013-0060-0}}</ref><ref name=Erythromycin>{{cite journal|last=Maheshwai|first=Nitin|title=Are young infants treated with erythromycin at risk for developing hypertrophic pyloric stenosis?|journal=Archives of Disease in Childhood|date=March 2007|volume=92|issue=3|pages=271–3|pmid=17337692|url=http://adc.bmj.com/content/92/3/271|accessdate=30 August 2012|doi=10.1136/adc.2006.110007|pmc=2083424|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107021907/http://adc.bmj.com/content/92/3/271|archive-date=2012-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。紅黴素屬於[[大環內酯|大環內酯]]類抗生素，會抑制細菌的蛋白質合成<ref name=AHFS2015/>。

<!-- History, society and culture -->
紅黴素於1952年首次从一种放線菌：{{le|糖多孢红霉菌|Saccharopolyspora erythraea}}（{{lang-la|Saccharopolyspora erythraea}}）中純化出來<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref>{{cite book|last1=Vedas|first1=J. C.|name-list-format=vanc|title=Biosynthesis : polyketides and vitamins|date=2000|publisher=Springer|location=Berlin [u.a.]|isbn=9783540669692|page=52|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=XUuFPxvfWgAC&pg=PA52|access-date=2016-08-24|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927165149/https://books.google.ca/books?id=XUuFPxvfWgAC&pg=PA52|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本品列名於[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]之中，為基礎公衛體系必備藥物之一<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of Essential Medicines|format=PDF|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423005004/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該藥屬於[[學名藥|學名藥]]，價格不貴<ref name=Ric2013>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richard J.|name-list-format=vanc|title=Tarascon pocket pharmacopoeia|date=2013|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|location=[Sudbury, Mass.]|isbn=9781449673611|page=72|edition=2013 delux lab-coat ed., 14th|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=zJay-fZCFGgC&pg=PA72|access-date=2016-08-24|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305042644/https://books.google.ca/books?id=zJay-fZCFGgC&pg=PA72|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本品在[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]的每錠批發價約於 0.03 至 0.06 [[美元|USD]]之間<ref name=ERC2015>{{cite web|title=Erythromycin|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=ERY250T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=250%20mg&desc=Erythromycin&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=06%2E2%2E2%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2806%2E2%2E2%2E%29Other%20antibacterials%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=23 August 2015}}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。
